<div class="modal fade" id="roleInfoModal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="roleInfoModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="modal-dialog modal-lg">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header bg-primary text-white">
        <h5 class="modal-title fw-bold" id="roleInfoModalLabel">
          <i class="fas fa-info-circle me-2"></i>
          Role Management Guide
        </h5>
        <button type="button" class="btn-close btn-close-white" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <div class="alert alert-primary mb-4">
          <h4 class="alert-heading d-flex align-items-center">
            <i class="fas fa-info-circle me-2"></i>
            About Role Management
          </h4>
          <hr>
          <p class="mb-0">
            This dashboard allows administrators to assign and remove user roles, controlling access and permissions within the server.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card border-primary mb-4">
          <div class="card-header bg-light">
            <i class="fas fa-columns me-2"></i> Table Columns Explanation
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card border-success h-100">
                  <div class="card-header bg-success bg-opacity-10 text-success">
                    <i class="fas fa-check-circle me-2"></i> Basic Information
                  </div>
                  <div class="card-body">
                    <ul class="mb-0">
                      <li><strong>User ID:</strong> Unique identifier for the user</li>
                      <li><strong>User Name:</strong> Display name of the user</li>
                      <li><strong>App Group ID:</strong> Identifier for the application group</li>
                      <li><strong>Role:</strong> Specific role assigned to the user</li>
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card border-info h-100">
                  <div class="card-header bg-info bg-opacity-10 text-info">
                    <i class="fas fa-chart-bar me-2"></i> Additional Information
                  </div>
                  <div class="card-body">
                    <ul class="mb-0">
                      <li><strong>Registered:</strong> Date and time when the role was assigned</li>
                      <li><strong>Actions:</strong> Controls for removing roles</li>
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card border-warning mb-4">
          <div class="card-header bg-light">
            <i class="fas fa-tools me-2"></i> Available Actions
          </div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-6 mb-3 mb-md-0">
                <div class="card h-100">
                  <div class="card-header bg-primary bg-opacity-10 text-primary">
                    <i class="fas fa-user-plus me-2"></i> Add Role
                  </div>
                  <div class="card-body">
                    <p>Assign a new role to a user using the form at the bottom of the dashboard. Requires User ID, User Center, App Group ID, and Role ID.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="card h-100">
                  <div class="card-header bg-danger bg-opacity-10 text-danger">
                    <i class="fas fa-trash-alt me-2"></i> Remove Role
                  </div>
                  <div class="card-body">
                    <p>Remove an assigned role from a user. The role will be immediately revoked from the user's permissions.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="alert alert-warning">
          <h5 class="alert-heading d-flex align-items-center">
            <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle me-2"></i>
            Important Notes
          </h5>
          <hr>
          <ul class="mb-0">
            <li>Role changes are applied immediately and do not require a service restart</li>
            <li>Ensure the correct User ID and App Group ID are provided to avoid errors</li>
            <li>Removing a role is permanent; reassign it if needed</li>
            <li>Roles are stored in <strong>RoleDB</strong> and managed via <strong>RoleSrv</strong> (Current version: <%= currentVersion %>, Status: <%= serviceStatus %>)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">
          <i class="fas fa-check-circle me-1"></i> Understood
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>